    <briefdescription>
<para>Token bucket rate limiter — header-only. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Throttle operations to N-per-second. Classic use cases: limit log output, throttle retransmissions, cap sensor poll rate.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Usage</title><para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="structSYN__RateLimit" kindref="compound">SYN_RateLimit</ref><sp/>rl;</highlight></codeline>
